add table ip ferm
delete table ip ferm
add table ip ferm
add chain ip ferm INPUT { type filter hook input priority 0; }
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 22 reject
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 23 reject with icmp type host-unreachable
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 25 log
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 26 log prefix "drop: "
add rule ip ferm INPUT limit rate 5/second accept
